
Please create two classes that demonstrate the following:

1) A static method calling another static method in the same class DONE
2) A static method calling a non-static method in the same class DONE
3) A static method calling a static method in another class DONE
4) A static method calling a non-static method in another class DONE
5) A non-static method calling a non-static method in the same class DONE
6) A non-static method calling a non-static method in another class DONE
7) A non-static method calling a static method in the same class DONE
8) A non-static method calling a static method in another class DONE
